<p><i>The below is an open page collecting oppositional arguments against the <a href="/wiki/Licensing_update" title="Licensing update">licensing update</a>. Some comments from the Wikimedia Foundation can be found on the <a href="/wiki/Talk:Licensing_update/Questions_and_Answers/Oppositional_arguments" title="Talk:Licensing update/Questions and Answers/Oppositional arguments">discussion page</a>. Any editor is able to present their views on the topics at hand; in doing so, such editors represent themselves only.</i>
