<h3 data-mw-thread-id="h-Why_shouldn&#039;t_the_projects_be_released_into_the_public_domain?-Community_commentary-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z"><span id="Why_shouldn.27t_the_projects_be_released_into_the_public_domain.3F"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Why_shouldn't_the_projects_be_released_into_the_public_domain?"><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="h-Why_shouldn't_the_projects_be_released_into_the_public_domain?-Community_commentary-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z"></span>Why shouldn't the projects be released into the public domain?<span data-mw-comment-end="h-Why_shouldn't_the_projects_be_released_into_the_public_domain?-Community_commentary-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z"></span></span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Licensing_update/Questions_and_Answers/Oppositional_arguments&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: Why shouldn&#039;t the projects be released into the public domain?"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z-Why_shouldn't_the_projects_be_released_into_the_public_domain?"></span>What are the arguments against doing this?  <a href="/wiki/User:Pie4all88" title="User:Pie4all88">Pie4all88</a> <a href="https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Licensing_update/Questions_and_Answers/Oppositional_arguments#c-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z-Why_shouldn't_the_projects_be_released_into_the_public_domain?" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">20:05, 14 April 2009 (UTC)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z-Why_shouldn't_the_projects_be_released_into_the_public_domain?"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z","author":"Pie4all88","type":"comment","level":1,"id":"c-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z-Why_shouldn't_the_projects_be_released_into_the_public_domain?","replies":["c-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z-Why_shouldn't_the_projects_be_released_into_the_public_domain?"></span>
</p>
<dl><dd><i><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z"></span>That</i> is simply not legallly possible... Why Wales didn't choose PD in the first place, I do not know, but unfortunately we have to stand this (of course, there might be some good arguments of not choosing PD). <a href="/wiki/User:Calandrella" title="User:Calandrella">Calandrella</a> <a href="https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Licensing_update/Questions_and_Answers/Oppositional_arguments#c-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">20:38, 14 April 2009 (UTC)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z","author":"Calandrella","type":"comment","level":2,"id":"c-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z","replies":["c-Ksd5-2009-05-04T20:19:00.000Z-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z","c-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T21:03:00.000Z-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T20:05:00.000Z"></span>
<dl><dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Ksd5-2009-05-04T20:19:00.000Z-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z"></span>He didn't choose PD because it wouldn't be a good business model. Attribution wouldn't be required, so people would start ripping the content and saying it's their own. There are other arguments as well. <a href="/wiki/User:Ksd5" class="mw-redirect" title="User:Ksd5">Ksd5</a> <a href="https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Licensing_update/Questions_and_Answers/Oppositional_arguments#c-Ksd5-2009-05-04T20:19:00.000Z-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">20:19, 4 May 2009 (UTC)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Ksd5-2009-05-04T20:19:00.000Z-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2009-05-04T20:19:00.000Z","author":"Ksd5","type":"comment","level":3,"id":"c-Ksd5-2009-05-04T20:19:00.000Z-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z","replies":[]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Ksd5-2009-05-04T20:19:00.000Z-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z"></span></dd>
<dd><span data-mw-comment-start="" id="c-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T21:03:00.000Z-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z"></span>True, but I imagine Richard Stallman could write another loophole into the GFDL to make it legal.  Alternately, we could petition for a Creative Commons license that does not require attribution, which would essentially be the same thing.  <a href="/wiki/User:Pie4all88" title="User:Pie4all88">Pie4all88</a> <a href="https://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Licensing_update/Questions_and_Answers/Oppositional_arguments#c-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T21:03:00.000Z-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z" class="ext-discussiontools-init-timestamplink">21:03, 14 April 2009 (UTC)</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-buttons" data-mw-thread-id="c-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T21:03:00.000Z-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z"><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">[</span><a class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-reply" role="button" tabindex="0" href="">reply</a><span class="ext-discussiontools-init-replylink-bracket">]</span><!--__DTELLIPSISBUTTON__{"threadItem":{"timestamp":"2009-04-14T21:03:00.000Z","author":"Pie4all88","type":"comment","level":3,"id":"c-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T21:03:00.000Z-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z","replies":["c-Kushal_one-2009-04-14T23:12:00.000Z-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T21:03:00.000Z","c-Cbrown1023-2009-04-14T21:23:00.000Z-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T21:03:00.000Z"]}}--></span><span data-mw-comment-end="c-Pie4all88-2009-04-14T21:03:00.000Z-Calandrella-2009-04-14T20:38:00.000Z"></span>
